Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.18,0:00:37.89,Default,,0,0,0,,As of this moment, the ESP Research Society is officially disbanding!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.51,0:00:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What{\i0}?!
