Dialogue: 1,0:02:12.23,0:02:16.24,Titles,,0,0,0,,{\an1\pos(144,880)\fad(250,250)\shad0\blur0.6\fsp-2\fscx78}I Want You To Know
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.69,0:02:14.94,Default,,0,53,0,,{\an3}Pull yourself together, Kotoura!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.11,0:02:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,My home...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.11,0:02:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no good. We've lost her!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.66,0:02:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What do I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.91,0:02:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Don't die, Kotoura!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.75,0:02:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I must give her mouth-to-mouth!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.17,0:02:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.92,0:02:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I must perform chest compressions!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.25,0:02:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}How am I supposed to choose?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.13,0:02:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! I can just choose {\i1}both{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.55,0:02:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Kotoura.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.60,0:02:46.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't let my guard down for a second around this Lothario.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.48,0:02:50.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Feels like it's been ages since you've called me that!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.23,0:02:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It kinda makes me tingle!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.48,0:02:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Ever the peerless lecher.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.36,0:02:56.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you quite finished with your little hymeneal comedy routine?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.44,0:02:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hymeneal?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.11,0:02:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.86,0:03:00.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you {\i1}think{\i0} that word means?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.49,0:03:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,That is—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.78,0:03:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,what do you mean, "disbanding," President Mifune?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.66,0:03:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly what I mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.33,0:03:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The activities of the ESP Society,\N directed at demonstrating scientifically
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.08,0:03:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,the existence of psychic powers and encouraging their acceptance
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.54,0:03:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,among the general populace, are ending as of today.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.96,0:03:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you serious about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.34,0:03:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.76,0:03:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Kotoura.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.67,0:03:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And, as of today,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.47,0:03:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm proudly announcing the foundation of the New ESP Research Society!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.26,0:03:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.31,0:03:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You heard me. The New ESP Society!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.27,0:03:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Its primary aim will be to have fun with a psychic.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.06,0:03:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,,A psychic?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.94,0:03:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.44,0:03:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll tease Kotoura and laugh at her ridiculous reactions.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.61,0:03:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Pretty much the same stuff we did before.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.11,0:03:45.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Why must everyone mock me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.45,0:03:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, so this means it's okay for me to stay here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.58,0:03:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.75,0:03:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Your home isn't going away.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.75,0:03:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, good grief.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.63,0:03:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You might've said so in the first place...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.71,0:04:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang on, couldn't you hear Yuriko thinking about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.34,0:04:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You know you can't trust what she actually {\i1}says{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.05,0:04:05.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got quite the wicked tongue yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.14,0:04:09.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I was so shocked, I didn't have time to check her thoughts.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.97,0:04:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like you guys saw through her, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.81,0:04:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,So it takes much lewder and lustier thoughts
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.19,0:04:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,to pique your interest, does it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.73,0:04:20.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, damn! My manly spirit is rising!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.19,0:04:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,If I rig a hidden camera in that haunted house on Third Street
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.40,0:04:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,and lure Kotoura there...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.24,0:04:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm on the fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.70,0:04:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew I could trust you two to swiftly grasp the New ESP Society's objectives.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.62,0:04:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Stop picking on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.79,0:04:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You make a fine team, Manabe and Moritani.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.63,0:04:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You're getting along a lot better than you were.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.80,0:04:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like you've lost your hesitation.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.14,0:04:49.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm sorry. Kotoura has all my love.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.89,0:04:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't reciprocate your feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.10,0:04:53.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.64,0:04:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I {\i0}knew{\i1} it would end this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.53,0:05:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,And so, to celebrate the creation of the New ESP Society,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.61,0:05:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,shall we sing some karaoke?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.03,0:05:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yippee!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.53,0:05:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah. You all went to karaoke before I joined the club.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.66,0:05:14.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Come with us, Moritani.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.91,0:05:17.29,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Sure. Let's sing together.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.54,0:05:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll regret those words.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.92,0:05:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You're horrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.67,0:05:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, sorry. I need to finish something off here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.55,0:05:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Kotoura, would you mind helping me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.80,0:05:28.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.51,0:05:31.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we'll head on over and reserve a room.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.89,0:05:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's scoot, you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.22,0:05:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What? I can help too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.39,0:05:36.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, we should all...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.52,0:05:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't dawdle. Let's get moving, Moritani.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.82,0:05:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what are you doing? Stop shoving!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.03,0:05:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't go overboard, Yuriko.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.41,0:05:58.62,Default,,0,0,0,,President Mifune, everything's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.29,0:06:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,There was never any need for you to do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.80,0:06:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, no more apologizing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.47,0:06:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,In your every glance, I've heard an apology.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.18,0:06:15.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You apologized in tears, and apologized in laughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.02,0:06:17.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough. No more remorse.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.10,0:06:21.11,Default,,0,0,0,,But I've been trying to use you all along!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.56,0:06:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.61,0:06:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I pretended to be a good mentor,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.94,0:06:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,but I only wanted to control you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.74,0:06:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.57,0:06:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I showed you terrible things just to get your sympathy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.53,0:06:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.53,0:06:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I put you in danger on my mother's account,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.58,0:06:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,even though she had nothing to do with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.25,0:06:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I know all of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.83,0:06:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I {\i1}am{\i0} a psychic.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.79,0:06:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Then how can you say I needn't apologize?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.92,0:06:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been a terrible friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.22,0:06:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just a dirty selfish—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.63,0:06:52.22,Alt,,0,0,0,,I have no right to condemn you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.51,0:06:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, I was only using you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.56,0:06:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Kotoura.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.81,0:07:01.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for giving me
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.48,0:07:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,such a wonderful place to be myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.28,0:07:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Some president I am, letting you see me like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.16,0:07:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,But are you really giving up on proving that psychic abilities exist?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.54,0:07:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd be lying if I said I had found some sort of catharsis.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.96,0:07:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,But I can't let Muroto get hurt again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.29,0:07:26.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll just take it slow and do what I can to—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.26,0:07:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What the heck is {\i1}that{\i0} look?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.88,0:07:33.89,Default,,0,0,0,,So that really was what was going on with you and Muroto!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.89,0:07:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean, "what was going on"?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.64,0:07:38.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly what I mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.18,0:07:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,So you wanna hear alllll about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.35,0:07:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Shoot! I'm in for it now!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.61,0:07:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay. You can read my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.86,0:07:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Go on. Look all you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.15,0:07:50.61,Default,,0,0,0,,U-Um.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.61,0:07:53.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's right. We can't let Manabe and the other wai—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.12,0:07:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Do it{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.95,0:07:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.12,0:08:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sorry you had to see me like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.33,0:08:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nah, it's normal for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.62,0:08:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That was your cue to say something nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.96,0:08:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That aside,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.34,0:08:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You said that you'd stay with me until we reached port,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.34,0:08:14.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}that you'd always be at my side.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.14,0:08:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.35,0:08:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So how exactly did you mean that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.35,0:08:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Well, we're childhood friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.44,0:08:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And I don't have any plans to move away just yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.31,0:08:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Um. I am truly sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.07,0:08:30.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.61,0:08:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,That lunkhead is genuinely clueless!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.07,0:08:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been subtly seducing him for frickin' {\i1}years{\i0},
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.45,0:08:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,and he doesn't even notice!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.24,0:08:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Please calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.54,0:08:43.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I'm just used to it at this point.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.79,0:08:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take this slow too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.79,0:08:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You and Manabe, though!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.25,0:08:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You two are total lovebirds!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.01,0:08:51.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.30,0:08:55.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Please stop picking on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.43,0:08:57.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Knowing Manabe,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.14,0:08:59.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll bet he's constantly whispering amorous nothings in your ear.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.97,0:09:02.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Absolutely not!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.35,0:09:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.64,0:09:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Manabe's never—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.06,0:09:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,He's never...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.35,0:09:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.52,0:09:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Kotoura?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.65,0:09:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I've just realized Manabe
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.44,0:09:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,has never actually {\i1}said{\i0} "I love you."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.24,0:09:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's be off! Everyone is waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.91,0:09:25.79,Default,,0,0,0,,That's just no fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.50,0:09:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, my throat is shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.42,0:09:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You sang too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.17,0:09:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And you're as tone deaf as ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.97,0:09:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Back then you taught me the strength to live
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.30,0:09:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,and the meaning to it all,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.52,0:09:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,and I embrace it with all my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.48,0:09:50.73,Default,,0,0,0,,So that in all things around us
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.48,0:09:54.53,Default,,0,0,0,,The flowers of hope may bloom,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.86,0:09:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\a6\i1}What? What? Is this a joke?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.53,0:09:59.57,Default,,0,0,0,,We start our days together here
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.11,0:09:59.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\a6\i0}Huh? Huh? Huh? Huh? Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.82,0:10:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,We start our days together here
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.00,0:10:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\a6\i1}Absolutely unbearable!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.00,0:10:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you are. Chin up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.59,0:10:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.88,0:10:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Welp, see ya tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.97,0:10:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,M-Manabe!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.51,0:10:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Um. Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.60,0:10:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Night!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.15,0:10:33.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why should he need to say it out loud?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.77,0:10:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I know how he feels, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.36,0:10:37.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.20,0:10:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I must have left the lights on this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.70,0:10:43.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna drive up my electricity bill.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.53,0:10:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be stingy over stupid little things like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.04,0:10:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I live on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.62,0:10:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to economize wherever I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.92,0:10:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What? When did you start living like you're poor?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.04,0:10:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not poor, simply prudent.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.88,0:10:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.67,0:10:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,M-Mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.47,0:11:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,So. Why are you here today?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.10,0:11:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,How did you get into my room?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.39,0:11:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I came to eat at a restaurant by here, but it was closed. That's {\i1}all{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.90,0:11:12.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I had the landlord unlock the door for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.27,0:11:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.98,0:11:16.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You know you're a pretty crappy host?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.57,0:11:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,At least offer me some food and booze.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.03,0:11:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,But, well, I'm not old enough to drink, so I don't have any alcohol.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.20,0:11:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.83,0:11:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go buy some right now. Please wait here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.66,0:11:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.04,0:11:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm coming too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.13,0:11:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.46,0:11:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You really are a damn idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.01,0:11:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's well after dark. She can't go out alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.57,0:12:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,So how is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.74,0:12:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess it's not inedible.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.99,0:12:04.91,Default,,0,0,0,,When did you learn to make this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.45,0:12:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I tried to make it how you used to.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.16,0:12:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.54,0:12:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You used to cook it for me all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.08,0:12:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Guess I forgot.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.83,0:12:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.17,0:12:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What's eating you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.01,0:12:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing. It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.80,0:12:25.84,Default,,0,0,0,,My daughter, ever trying to avoid a conflict.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.84,0:12:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Pathetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.97,0:12:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,,And yet every time you open your mouth, you say something insensitive and piss people off.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.27,0:12:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You say you made friends, but that's got to be a bunch of bullshit.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.73,0:12:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It is {\i1}not{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.24,0:12:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,They've stayed by my side! Supported me!\N They're true friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.53,0:12:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I am {\i1}not{\i0} lying!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.33,0:12:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, you—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.12,0:12:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You abandoned your own child in her greatest need!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.00,0:12:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You have no right to talk like you know me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.42,0:12:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Wha?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.17,0:13:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! Like you're the only one capable of feeling pain!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.38,0:13:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't forget about those who were hurt just because they got close you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.09,0:13:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,If it was too much for you, why not ask for help?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.47,0:13:12.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Or could it be {\i1}you{\i0} didn't have any friends, Mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.14,0:13:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.35,0:13:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.31,0:13:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.48,0:13:21.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You're just a naïve little girl with crappy taste in boys!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.07,0:13:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I know Manabe's a hopeless lecher!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.11,0:13:26.82,Default,,0,0,0,,But look who's talking!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.82,0:13:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't forgotten that Tsuyama guy you were with!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.99,0:13:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.12,0:13:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You ignorant brat! Don't you take that tone with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.37,0:13:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Speak for yourself! Some adult you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.33,0:13:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it! Get over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.46,0:13:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Why I'll—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.30,0:13:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother, you {\i1}nincompoop{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.34,0:13:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.68,0:13:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Nincompoop! {\alpha&HFF&}Nincompoop! Nincompoop!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.72,0:13:53.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Nincompoop! Nincompoop! {\alpha&HFF&}Nincompoop!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.85,0:13:54.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Nincompoop! Nincompoop! Nincompoop!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.43,0:13:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You little...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.52,0:13:58.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Cut it out right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.31,0:13:59.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You{\i0} cut it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.73,0:14:01.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You pelican daughter!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.27,0:14:02.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You nincompoop mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.03,0:14:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,How did you turn out like this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.90,0:14:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all your fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.28,0:14:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn, you've really learned to dish it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.12,0:14:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,My friends told me I shouldn't bottle up my feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.79,0:14:20.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Friends, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.88,0:14:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,So what were you going to say about Tsuyama?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.71,0:14:27.09,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.01,0:14:29.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hi there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.47,0:14:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So you're Kumiko's daughter?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.26,0:14:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}High school girl sighted!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.97,0:14:38.02,Default,,0,0,0,,That filthy pedophile!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.02,0:14:40.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Why didn't you tell me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.81,0:14:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the one who told me to stay quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.77,0:14:46.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Did I say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.07,0:14:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess we really do share a lousy taste in men.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.28,0:14:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I think you've still got me beat.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.41,0:14:52.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I gotta some more booze in me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.91,0:14:55.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Haruka, clean up and get the sake ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.45,0:14:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You could help out too, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.50,0:15:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't you say you'd do all the cooking and cleaning when I left home?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.84,0:15:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I think that offer is no longer valid.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.47,0:15:10.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, Mother, I'm finished cleaning.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.51,0:15:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Just give me—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.72,0:15:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Honestly, Mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.73,0:15:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Haruka.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.90,0:15:24.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.57,0:15:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If only you had never been born.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.53,0:15:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Wait, Kumiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.91,0:15:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}K-Kumiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.21,0:15:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm sorry I was so weak, Haruka.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.00,0:15:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,1000)\i1}I'm so sorry I couldn't protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.63,0:15:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.18,0:15:55.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I was such a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.97,0:15:58.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My power didn't help me look {\i0}inside{\i1}.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.43,0:16:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I didn't even try to understand what my mother was really feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.48,0:16:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why did she put up that cold front?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.15,0:16:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I never knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.19,0:16:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I never knew there were things I couldn't understand without words.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.09,0:16:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Mama.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.30,0:16:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like my eggs over easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.81,0:16:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.48,0:16:49.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.58,0:17:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I asked for over easy, Mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.21,0:17:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,These are so overcooked they're bitter.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.96,0:17:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry I'm late.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.84,0:17:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,So I gather you told Kumiko about that incident with the criminal?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.26,0:17:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't a clue what you mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.68,0:17:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I just got a message from Haruka.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.55,0:17:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,From Haruka?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.26,0:17:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, look at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.77,0:17:26.19,Chalkbaofaura,,0,0,0,,{\move(1029.33,601.335,981.54,-1.245)\fry5\fscx120\fscy110\blur0.7\alpha&H11&\fax0.05\frz0.5273}Haruka
Dialogue: 2,0:17:21.77,0:17:26.19,Chalkbaofaura,,0,0,0,,{\fry6\fscx120\fscy110\fax0.03\blur0.7\alpha&H11&\frz0.567\fs30\move(1238.84,728.34,1190.91,127.27,21,4400)}Mom's
Dialogue: 2,0:17:21.77,0:17:26.19,Chalkbaofaura,,0,0,0,,{\fry6\fscx120\fscy110\fax0.03\blur0.7\alpha&H11&\frz0.567\fs30\move(1239.5,752.34,1191.58,151.27,21,4400)}fried
Dialogue: 2,0:17:21.77,0:17:26.19,Chalkbaofaura,,0,0,0,,{\fry6\fscx120\fscy110\fax0.03\blur0.7\alpha&H11&\frz0.567\fs30\move(1239.5,774.34,1191.58,173.27,21,4400)}eggs
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.35,0:17:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmph. Her cooking used to be a lot better.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.65,0:17:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,That idiot daughter of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.19,0:17:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Kotoura, let's head to club.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.74,0:17:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Manabe.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.07,0:17:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,KotoUra!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.49,0:17:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,For goodness' sakes open the door! He's right behind you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.54,0:17:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Please stop casting me in your weird fantasies.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.62,0:17:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got something to do, so you go on ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.71,0:17:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.63,0:17:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,So, Moritani, I wanted to talk to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.76,0:17:58.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. He hasn't actually told you himself, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.39,0:18:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,But don't you know what's in his heart?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.43,0:18:05.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't see any cause for worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.77,0:18:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I thought it was okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.64,0:18:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,But then I realized it:
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.52,0:18:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,sometimes I need people to tell me what they're thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.65,0:18:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to hear it in Manabe's own words.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.11,0:18:17.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.24,0:18:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,So you came to me for advice.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.82,0:18:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I know it's kind of awful for me to ask you of all people about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.91,0:18:26.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about that. I'm over it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.75,0:18:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Honestly, it'd just make me happy to help a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.25,0:18:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Moritani.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.09,0:18:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't expect any stellar advice, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.88,0:18:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Manabe only gave me a serious answer because I confessed to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.30,0:18:43.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I think you'll have to put your own feelings into words first.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.60,0:18:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,,R-Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.85,0:18:48.77,Default,,0,0,0,,But I've never confessed to anyone before.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.19,0:18:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What do I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.48,0:18:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll just have to practice!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.61,0:18:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Imagine I'm Manabe and confess to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.78,0:18:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.74,0:19:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I... I l-lo—
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.24,0:19:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,All finished, Kotoura?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.95,0:19:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I love you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.12,0:19:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.95,0:19:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,M-Manabe?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.70,0:19:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.42,0:19:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Moritani, that was sinfully divine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.92,0:19:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll make sure you can never so much as look at a mere boy again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.26,0:19:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,,My woman's been stolen by another woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.93,0:19:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,How can this simultaneously feel so unnatural
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.01,0:19:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,and yet so! Damn! Good!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.27,0:19:30.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.85,0:19:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me take care of him. Carry on.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.36,0:19:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.15,0:19:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Kotoura, your attempts at \Nself-expression tend to backfire,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.44,0:19:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,so I think you'll be better off saying\N whatever comes to mind at the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.03,0:19:43.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.62,0:19:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you be so sharp when it comes to everyone but yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.83,0:19:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Are you mad about something?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.62,0:19:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.04,0:19:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Sto-O-op!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.17,0:19:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,So there you have it. What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.96,0:20:00.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I get the feeling it'll work out somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.80,0:20:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.93,0:20:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.89,0:20:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,That's my best friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.22,0:20:08.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Wait! We're best friends, aren't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.64,0:20:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\i1}Sorry. Not anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.31,0:20:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, sorry! Did I hurt you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.61,0:20:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.23,0:20:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Moritani.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.57,0:20:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Score!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.70,0:20:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.12,0:20:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Christmas already? Time really flies.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.25,0:20:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Manabe, it's a white Christma—
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.05,0:20:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yippee! Snow! Snow!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.84,0:20:46.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Kotoura! You think it'll stick?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.09,0:20:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's have a snowball battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.72,0:20:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,And then build a ginormous snowman!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.31,0:20:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You really follow your heart, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.61,0:21:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I love you, Manabe.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.61,0:21:04.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm actually embarrassed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.61,0:21:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I say it all the time, so that's only natural,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.20,0:21:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,but this is the first time you've said it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.24,0:21:10.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.45,0:21:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.37,0:21:15.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You've never said it to me, Manabe.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.21,0:21:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never said it out loud?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.79,0:21:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I've never said it out loud?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.67,0:21:28.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Kotoura. I'm thinking it every second of the day, so I had no idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.47,0:21:30.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't life a funny thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.39,0:21:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Even you can't be thinking it {\i1}every{\i0} second!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.39,0:21:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you get how much it's been bothering me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.60,0:21:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's the way you are, Manabe.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.23,0:21:40.65,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the way I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.36,0:21:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I love you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.28,0:21:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I've always, always loved you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.32,0:21:48.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I love you like crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.58,0:21:52.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you hear what was in my heart that time?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.08,0:21:54.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I did. I heard everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.41,0:21:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.63,0:22:15.73,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(650,300)\fsp-1.5\blur2}How do you stand again when something trips you up?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.94,0:22:28.61,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,500)\fsp-1.5\blur2}Can truth be found by thinking about the days to come?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:28.66,0:22:36.83,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)\fsp-1.5\blur2}We all come into this world alone when we are born,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.50,0:22:38.33,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\fsp-1.5\blur2}and precisely because of that,
Dialogue: 1,0:22:38.00,0:22:45.38,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\fsp-1.5\blur2}we try to live life with others from then on
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.26,0:22:53.68,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\fsp-1.5\blur2}Back then you taught me the strength to live and the meaning to it all,
Dialogue: 1,0:22:53.39,0:22:59.02,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\fsp-1.5\blur2}and I embrace it with all my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.81,0:23:05.57,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\fsp-1.5\blur2}So that in all things around us the flower of hope may bloom,
Dialogue: 1,0:23:05.28,0:23:11.36,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,500)\fsp-1.5\blur2}we start our days together here
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.49,0:23:18.00,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,525)\fsp-1.5\blur2}We start our days together here
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.50,0:23:27.01,Default,,0,53,0,,{\an9}Kotoura!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.50,0:23:27.01,Default,,53,0,0,,{\an7}Kotoura!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.50,0:23:27.01,Default,,53,0,0,,{\an1}Kotoura!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.50,0:23:27.01,Default,,0,53,0,,{\an3}Kotoura!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.17,0:23:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning, everyone!
